UID:10001906-1776344400-1776353400@www.culturelink.ca
SUMMARY:Networking Event with TD Canada Trust
DESCRIPTION:Meet and network with representatives from TD Canada Trust. \n\nLearn about the industry\nMake connections with people working in your desired role\nReceive advise for your job search\n\nParticipants must be: \n\nInternational trained professionals\nPermanent Residents or Convention Refugees\nAt least 19 years old\nJob-ready English proficiency level\n\nTo participate\, fill in the Registration Form. \nFor more information\, contact Rubina at rafsar@culturelink.ca or Victor at vgomes@culturelink.ca.
URL:https://www.culturelink.ca/event/networking-event-with-td-canada-trust-2026-04-16/
LOCATION:CultureLink\, 2340 Dundas St W\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6P\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.culturelink.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Adults-Mentorship-and-Networking-CultureLink-Icon.jpg
END:VEVENT
