SUMMARY:Citizenship Education Circle - North York Central Library
DESCRIPTION:Free weekly sessions to prepare for the Citizenship test. \n\nLearn about the test’s content and structure\nGet support and tips from our Volunteer Mentors\nPractice with sample quizzes\n\nFor Permanent Residents and Convention Refugees. \nTo participate\, fill out our Registration Form\, or contact Lily at lkrowiak@culturelink.ca.
